detailed_reviews.review_text: Great Toddler/Mommy McDs with large, enclosed play place, climbing structure 2y+, ordering/pay station inside play area, high chairs, NO wifi access, bathroom not in play area, & dirty but not horrid. They had pancakes allday in happy meal & lots of parking. I d recommend, if you need a place to work & eat , while children run in circles screaming. There are many screaming children. Kid-friendliness: Bathrooms, enclosed play area, large climbing structure with slide & padded area. 2yr -12yrs, high chairs, room for strollers, trash, bathrooms Wheelchair accessibility: All on one level, handicapped parking, room in restaurant for wheelchairs

This McDonalds has a great location spot next to Science World and the stadium. Surprisingly, it has free parking with a big parking lot. Its open 24/7 for dine in, take out, and drive through. Kid-friendliness: Has an indoor playground

Well the reason Im giving them a 5 star is because there security caught the thief who actually stole the kids meal I had on the table so when I took little man I was looking after to the restroom so guy took his food and his box of doughnuts and actually drank out of my coffee cup but they handled with respect and I appreciated that from them plus the other people around us where super nice
It was fairly quick with a full line up frendly staff on the drive through

Consistently THE WORST drive thru service. I am asked to pull over and wait a minimum of 7 minutes every time I go. And every time, I have to walk in and demand my food...AND every single time the sauces I PAID FOR are not in the bag. The place is an absolute circus with food delivery guys, homeless, bums, addicted people lurking about everywhere. Its a zoo and the service is atrocious. Im DONE.
This Mc Donald center is fully automated. You can customize everything. Large variety in the menu and nice salad that I havent seen in any other branches before.
I have purchased 4 cars from these guys over the years and their service has been outstanding. I highly recommend them to anyone looking for a used car in excellent condition!!!!
Changed my life. The finest 5 star cuisine Ive ever had, how have I never heard of this place? Its like McMagic in my mouth!

In the middle of a heat dome and it was unbelievably hot outside ... walking into the restaurants lovely, air conditioned interior was such a relief! It was crazy busy and totally chaotic but all the staff we dealt with were so friendly and pleasant. There was lots of parking outside and no line-ups at the ordering kiosks and the washroom was spotless. Altogether a great visit.

Clean atmosphere. Not enough staff in the evening, for over a month now there has only been one cashier witch causes slower lines not everybody has a bank card to  pay with online. This also cause customers to get frustrated and angry and even sometimes cause a scene with staff members,  unfortunately One customer was extremely  frustrated he told a staff member to f@#(c) off and the staff member behind the counter said exactly the same words right back to the customer before he walked out.. I have Never experienced this at a McDonalds. Not the staff members fault but if there was more cashiers at the front maybe that could have been avoided.
The place  had a great experience with STAFF and Customers. Very nice,I will go Back.
Quick burger snack for lunch, always fast and tasty
Big place. Clean, I enjoy dine in

Been coming here every Saturday morning for breakfast, and every time I have quality service and food. There are mornings when the line up to the drive-thru is out to the street and we are only in line for 5 mins total and have our food. Other locations have us park and wait 10+ minutes even with no line. All employees work fast but politely. The food is always so fresh and hot. Could not recommend this location enough!
Great customer service. Went their around 12:15 and girl named Amrit took my order. She was really polite and humble. Great customer interaction.
This place is a zoo but they had shamrock shakes in may so they get 5 stars

As with most McDonalds, Ive had varied experiences but ill just share my most recent one as it was excellent.  The line up in the drive through was long and extended onto the street and through the parking lot. I couldnt believe how fast I got through, especially from ordering to payment to receiving my food. I thanked the lady for being so quick, and enjoyed my food which was hot and made how I asked. Yum!
Great food n drinks

Best thing about this particular McDonald would be the staff. From the Paladin guard that is always alert and courteously opens the door for customers to the guys in the kitchen. Ive dined here three times and each time these guys seem to actually enjoy doing their jobs. Big up to them
I got a shamrock McFlurry and it was great but man they gotta do something the atmosphere it felt like I was entering the bowels of the earth.
Good service. Tasty. Modest price
Fast friendly service and exactly what I ordered.  Great work team. Keep up the good work.

Very very friendly, efficient, & quick service. This drive through was what drive throughs should all be like. Correct order taking, very friendly & well spoken, good at up selling products, & making sure the customer gets the food hot, well prepared, & properly bagged. This was my best tasting, & well bagged Double Quarter Pounder with Cheese meal since the 1980s Special Kudos to this worker. Management should recognize her for her abilities & her #1 standards. ********** Stars for her

Its McDonalds the best munchies ever omnomnomn Vegetarian options: Theres beyond meat available Dietary restrictions: Fish allergens peanut allergens Parking: If your a customer you dont have to worry about paying for parking Kid-friendliness: No play place however theres an upstairs where kids can be loud and run around Wheelchair accessibility: Its ground level so no need to find a ramp

For the location and the how clean the restaurant is and the added security. It s a the only place I found that I can bring my small children into where no one is sleeping In the chair s Thanks again the people working in the back are amazing staff.
Today the chicken mcmuffin was the best I have ever had since it they came out both were very fresh. Soft cheese, soft muffin and tender chicken.  Congrats  well done. Keep it up.
I love the self checkout that they have, very convenient and theres never much of a wait even though tons of people were there!
Always got to love the artery clogging slopes that they serve here. May not be good for you but sure does taste delicious

After 1 year of lockdown been ( 2 yrs ) been to McD locations on Main! Have to say it was not a disppointment for an early dinner ( 2Can Dine coupon ). 1/4 pound cheese burger and also bought ( coupon ) 6 mini doughnuts ( acceptable, not the best compare to Cardems,Luckys doughnuts ) but its tasteful. The meals was amazing and its services! Worth the trip/back!
Very fast service . Food was actually put together properly and not sloppy. Like most other restaurants of the same.

Incident from 11th Nov. I wanted to thank the security guard from Paladin working that morning. Tall Indian Guy, He bravely defended us again 2 homeless people who were kicking our car doors and were threating us. He made sure we were safe and kicked them out. Thank you so much. I came to personally thank him multiple times but never saw him after that, as we rushed out that day, we were really scared. Thank you so much for your service.
Drive thru worker. Phenomenal
Great place to eat and love the staff

Used to work here, great people and managers. However dont stay after 10 pm, then its claimed by junkies. Watch for needles in washrooms, bags, crannies, toilet paper dispense. Also once saw a dude in the garbage compactor.
Its fast and good service

Its a McDonalds, but Im always amazed at how fast the drive through provides service. Good location (for McDonalds, lets not get me wrong here, its not good actual food). I fill my breakfast sandwich needs here regularly.
Best time to come to this location is late at night when theres only several groups dining and not a lot of people in line waiting for their food. The staff are very nice here.

Great service...Id ordered a double Big Mac and when I got to the Van to eat it with Rocky my pitbull...I found just a double burger not 4. I went back and they gave me my proper order and let me keep the double. Rocky real my enjoyed it.
Nice place
I ordered from Uber eats. Incredibly fast! My burger was made to my specifications. Perfectly. Lol thank you for my cookie! An excellent encounter! I love you guys!
The free fries are too good lol.. the new cigarettes
Great for a quick snack any time of the day. Menu as expected.
The staff are so aware and gracious I asked them for additional condiments and they immediately gave me Thank you so much I ll always buy from them

This used to be one of dirtiest McDonalds in north America due to homelessness and people with low personal care in its surroundings.  Washrooms where dirty, a lot of people very spending more than usual time in the lobby. BUT NOW!!!!!!!!! After having doors at its North West entrance closed, and having security at its main entrances, there are no more unrelated people hanging around. Even doordash and uber eats receive their deliveries from the security officer making it even more professional. Now I can tell the management worked hard to re- establish this place. I really hope this place holds their security officer which is very polite and professional. I also hope other McDonalds with busy downtown traffic to employ security officers , especially once covid is over and night clubs re opens.
Very consistent! I think they have yet to mess up my order and Ive visited this location MANY times. Plus the staff are friendly and have a great sense of urgency.
Quiet place. Nice view. For the rest, just an ordinary MacDonalds :)))
It was spectacular. Food elevates mood and the fine dining experience elevated me to hitherto unknown realms of clarity and inner peace.
My first experience with this restaurant was amazing but the location was great and easy for us to find and the price was great

I absolutely love McDonalds coffee and have no shame in saying it! Theyre coffee isnt too hot when you get it, and the taste is just so good! If youre ever looking for just a black coffee and dont want to break the bank..... Orrrr seriously just really want a good coffee, get theirs. I drink mine with 4 cream (yes, always and no it hasnt made me fat haha) I love that I buy 7 coffees and get a free one as well! The food is alright as well if you like carby stuff haha

[REVIEWED IN OCTOBER 2019] This McDonalds is a nice, large, but busy location, with plenty of comfortable seating areas to settle in. I came here & paid so I could use their WiFi to play World of Warcraft. Found out WoW was unplayable for whatever reason, despite other online games working okay. Rated 5 stars despite this disappointment, but its a pretty awesome McDonalds location. 24 hours at that!
It was nice but wierd. A stranger cleared it ,told me I should sit there, I ate my big Mac, ( alone but not) with barriers,I had a covid good time . I guess Today I made it to 59 yrs..

The paladins slinging grease in this citadel of soberiety are the last line of defense against the quarreling, drunken horde stumbling back toward the skytrain after striking out in Gastown. God bless them in their solemn duty.
This McDonalds food was pretty good. I liked my big Mac like I always get.  And always the best after a fat joint...
Great stop when walking along the creek because they have a washroom
Its nice and clean. The staff were all very friendly and helpful. McDonalds does everything right it seems!
This McDonalds is one of the best in Vancouver.  Very friendly and helpful staff provide a very pleasant overall order experience.  Keep up the great work
Nice day

Very sloppy burgers leaves you running straight to the bathroom! UPDATE: Since Ive last left this review. Ive notice that this particular McD has been making their burgers more with care, rather than the sloppy mess that i have been getting from here before.
Good location. Not much different than any other one but they are quick and give great service. Can get crazy busy at some hours.
Very well kept cleanliness of restaurant two thumbs up no mess ups on my order as well another plus

This location is one of the busiest McDonald s in town. I really give the employees credit for staying relatively cheerful throughout the day, even though this location gets quite a colourful variety of patrons.
I went thru the drive thru and it didnt take too long. The food was great service was good.

Oh man. Only come here if youre drunk or high. If youre sober, you better be going through the drive-thru. Otherwise, youll be seeing all the magnificent disgusting people who come here on Friday night on Wednesday afternoon.
Always fast. I order from the app and get it for pick up and its usually ready by the time Im there.
Not really sure why they were nervous during the work
Cause of whip cream on my hot cakes umm good
Very busy but fast service coffee was perfect they made it just right cause I like my coffee on the cold side thanks keep up the good work
Staff are great. They can handle the chaos...  Have always had a good experience here, order is always correct. Staff is kind and helpful
If you have kids. You can dine and let your kids play

The service is really good but the boys washroom is really dirty I am really scared of the washroom but the food and service is very very good the mangers are very nice also the soft serve ice cream that they make is really big and yummy
Excellent fast service. Cleaning person Wednesday am was very friendly and efficient. Meal was hot. Excellent all around outlet.
The seating situation has changed due to covid-19 but the place is very clean and hand sanitizer are everywhere and ready to be used.

Just love the service of this place....   I had a wound on my hand which started bleeding suddenly... So I asked them a band aid... Nd the staff nd the manager was so nice... That they offered me the first aid asap..  thank you so much for your help
Restaurant was clean first friendly service order was correct and served hot and fresh.
For lunch today, I had a Dijon Onion Burger, & it was delicious. It was only $2.99. I should have had two, however, as one wasnt quite enough to satisfy my hunger!
Busy restaurant with large parking lot. Staffs are friendly and efficient. Foods are within the standard. I appreciated and thanks they have a security guard in the restaurant.
Big one, not so clean    but cleaner than most others
Went thru the drive thru and the service was very fast and the staff were polite and they were able to get our whole order correct  :)
Bah dah dah daaah i am lovin it and alittle secret smiles are free;)
In near downtown, this is the best McDonalds. The most I like is, this has parking lot. The cons are you will see lots of homeless, washroom is dirty.
Dont know how long McDonalds have been in town but I was really surprised by how good the dining experience is. I think it will catch on.
Excellent quality control on the chicken nuggets. Consistently deliver a highly nutritious meal.
Busy, basic not trendy but they never let down.. good food and good service.
Food service is awesome and was clean in the dining area. Cant complain at all.
Outside clean washroom clean too good foods chicken  fish so good,coffee  can u make  a little hot drink better thx
Was pretty good they one of the good McDonalds around always clean and they treat the customer like customers no judgemental all
Despite location being somewhat sketchy, this location manages to keep clean and provide good service and food cooked to exacting standards.
Same McDonalds as everywhere. Crazy fast service and automated order kiosks everywhere! Kudos to the staff for being good at handling the local demographics of the DTES area.
probably the most cursed mcdonalds in Vancouver however immensely blessed at the same time
Surprisingly clean, staff must be incredibly patient. Theyve rarely ever messed up my order
The food is good love it its so awesome n the bigmac meal I love the most
Wonderful play structure my kids enjoy. Also, new upstairs dinning area is clean, and airly.
Friendly staff and good cooks. One of the best McDonalds in Greater Vancouver, conveniently located downtown by Science World, Via (train and bus station), Skytrain and close to Chinatown.
Gotta love McDonalds    Food was perfect as usual here too!
Lots of parking spaces. Clean place with security agent always available. Staff are quick and good in service.
All McDonalds are the same however this particular one has the highest ratio of junkie to staff in the Pacific Northwest. Thats a fact.
It was busy but staff were very efficient and organized.
Good location and good service even in the pandemic. Access to washroom too and security personnel by the entrance for assistance.
Dont blame them if youre fat.  They have salad and its not their fault if you dont choose it.
Prices have gone up since covid 19 but good food and good service

detailed_reviews.review_text: The service is fast and the food served is always fresh and hot. The self order checkout are easy to use and are always clean. The crew their is friendly and make sure that we understand what food we need and sometimes gives suggestions of what is better option. The dine in is cozy and wide especially in the sunshine it looks fabulous.

I usually pass by this McDonalds on the way to work using their mobile app which is very convenient. I usually use the drive-thru. The place looks neat and clean and the crew are very friendly, especially. Susan D Which is a delight to hear her in the drive-thru speaker and the window when youre passing through. Their coffee is very good as well as their muffins

The service is fast and the food served is always fresh and hot. The self order checkout are easy to use and are always clean. The crew their is friendly and make sure that we understand what food we need and sometimes gives suggestions of what is better option. The dine in is cozy and wide especially in the sunshine it looks fabulous. Recently they were giving free samples for their new ice cream and it was yummm. The parking lot has nice flowers and space for parking cars is wide. If I am nearby, I always get an ice cream for sure from here. The patio here though small is good for sitting during summer times.

google keeps asking me to review McDonalds even though this review means nothing to everyone everywhere. You all have an opinion on McDonalds and a strangers words on the internet isnt going to change that. I have attached a photo of one of my orders. I like ordering decaf completely black to see how the cashiers respond to the abomination. Thank you

Social distancing and limited seating in effect. Hand sanitizer at entrance/exit. Arrows to indicate traffic flow one way. Plexiglass shields at cashier as well as food pick up counter. All great safety measures to make you feel safe while ordering or eating here. Update:  service/atmosphere has gone downhill since reopening. Was there Friday night and took well over 6-7min to get my order. I ordered on the app. Restaurant was a mess. I could see kitchen was a mess too with fries all over the floor of the fry station. Staff was standing around chatting in kitchen and in no rush to serve customers. By the way, my fries were cold too. Very disappointed.
This place is well organized, very clean and with great customer service. First time 5 stars for McDonalds.

I bought for my kids lunch here a double burger and a happymeal.  But when I brought it home my son found it was a single burger. When I went to them the next day with a complaint, the administrator gave me a double burger and happymeal for free. A very positive experience. Thanks to the restaurant and manager.
Good placefor quick lunch and treat myself at the middle of the day.
good location, I have ordered McFish this time.. I can say it was not the freshest fried pattie, but I understand it was around 1.15am.. so no regrets.. it satisfied me and thats all what matter
Something about music list, whoever picked those songs, it s all contemporary and amazing as to make me stay for long and write reviews Cheers Food

Im giving this McDonalds 5 stars simply because I needed to blow my nose after getting off the bus and having to get on the SkyTrain.  Why didnt I just go to the Timmies literally just a few steps away right across the street from the SkyTrain station you ask?  Oh I did.  But sadly at 730am they had no toilet paper in their public washroom.  So, wtg, McDonalds!!; One more runny nose saved.  Thank you.
We went through the drive-thru and the attendant that was there, at about 9:00pm yesterday was really friendly and happy. The burger was made with care and was very full. Delightful experience.

Good food at reasonable prices and lots of free parking. Good for families on a budget especially when traveling or visiting Vancouver. Includes a playground for children. Vegetarian options: Special request menus available Dietary restrictions: Requests for special orders with extra veggies or salads are available Parking: Large lot for parking and other free parking on Southside of resturant Kid-friendliness: Lots of room for families and large seating areas, including playground. Wheelchair accessibility: Fully available
The time of your life. Amazing hamburger dish called a big mac. Im loving it. EAT IT. EAT THE THING. they also serve breakfast now. Im a physicist. Free refills kinda blew my mind. Food
When its raining and you just want some good vibes #McVibes
Excellent drive thru experience!! Fast and accurate order taking. Smiling faces order was perfectly placed in the bag. A, 7 star experience for sure!! Keep up the good work!!
Pretty convenient location. Friendly staff, 24 hours, so late night munchies are well taken care of.

Typical McDonalds franchise with a busy drive-through and large dine in area. Located on the busy Grandview Highway just down from the sky train station. This location is always exceedingly busy. Probably because of its excellent location close to transit and car thoroughfares. We went through drive-through today and even though the lineups were extensive through the double drive-through, service was efficient and accurate and the food was hot. What more can you expect from this staple of modern life?  Will come again.

We went by on the drive thru at 11pm, and the lady was so patient with us, even though we took forever to choose. Im very impressed by the customer service this late at night and with so many people lining up! Ill be coming back :))
Service was excellent and quality of food was great!

Small cafe with fresh food. Great quality and portion. I felt safe in there because they had the plexiglass installed in between tables. I ordered latte with oat milk and the crab cake brunch and chicken and bacon sandwich. Satisfied.

This was the first time I came for a visit with my friend. We  order two combos of fish burger and dine in there. The place was well cleaned and cozy.  We sat down, washed our hands in the washroom. Not for a while, the manager handed the meals to us with a smiling face. The food  was hot and delicious. Good to try again.

Take advantage of the awards points they offer check the app each day for new deals  . The workers are always very nice and pleasant  . Coffee muffin deal is the best with everything going up this pairing is the best option
Usually order from doordash here. Orders are always correct and arrive pretty fast, great job to all the workers here, it cant be easy getting everything done so fast in such a popular location.

For some reason the mcflurry in this mcdonalds costs less than the other mcdonalds I went to on that same day! This McDonalds also has more modern chairs and tables than some of the other ones Ive been to as they renovated a few years back.
Always clean, food comes out fresh and fast. Only knock off one star because the fries arent overfilling haha.
This is the most liminal McDonalds. 5 stars.

Best service around. These employees deserve a raise! On an extremely busy night they worked amazing as a team, were quick, efficient and werent messing up any orders. Plus they were cheering eachother on for doing a good job and getting through the rush and they deserve the claps
I had a Quarter Pounder BLT with large fries and a Coke. It was delicious. Tasty convenient food in a friendly atmosphere. Nice professional staff too.
They didn t have the item I asked but the guy in the front was very nice and gave me different options instead

Recently remodelled. Lots of kiosks not enough staff. Can take up to 10 minutes if you order during busy times.  Pickup area gets chaotic.  I dont like to get the toys with the Happy meals but they always include it. They try and have better managers than other locations.

i usually just order on skip, but i stopped at this location on my way home late around 11pm. I just want to say the two employees working, were very friendly and seemed to be enjoying doing their job.  Its often rare now days with covid and all, I just want to say thank you and keep up the good work LOL

Extremely polite young teens at drive thru. Way to go teens. So nice to see young people working hard and dispelling myths that they as a generation are video game addicts, rude and self centered with no manners. Keep up the good work McDonalds, and teens. It is well appreciated and noted

Very nice & cozy fast food restaurants. The staff at this McDonalds are very friendly & efficient compared to other locations. No fuss delicious hot & freshly prepared food. This is the first time in 15 years I have been served piping hot food to eat. Ideally,, by the time I get to my table, or the food gets brought to me in the car from Drive through, it is cold, the coffee tastes like Luke warm water & the pop is out of Gas. No wonder I hated McDonalds fast food. Believe me I truely enjoyed my meal today. Infact because I really enjoyed my meal today, we sat & also enjoyed Apple pies as an extra treat. I definately recommend all to try out this location, you will never again return to all those problem locations again. Very neat & cleans, no over flowing garbage bins or even a single dirty table, where customers had to clean, before eating their meals. Every single point at this location, was past excellent. Thank you McDonalds Restaurants.

Its McDonalds, so you know it is what it is. I didnt realise they dont sell their big salads anymore so thats kind of a bummer. The food was hot, fresh and fast. I got two cheese burgers and a poutine... the poutine has cheese curd! and a vanilla ice coffee. Overall happy with my order.
Completely surprising service. They were fast, polite, friendly, and best of all, got our entire order correct on the first attempt. For a second I almost thought I wasnt at a McDonalds!!
There are some great staff working here.
Great food, great service

My favorite McDonalds restaurant. They train all of the managers here and they always have all of the toys available for Happy Meals here because it is the head office. You will get impeccable service and top notch food quality here. Of course its still a McDonalds fast food burger, but within that category, its the best experience. Also the dining area is open 24 hours which is nice.
Well its hard time , but I know youre doing well . I love McDonalds Restaurants.

Thank you midnight team for preparing my midnight meal lol You guys did a excellent job :) I always order from Skip during 1am or 2am, if you guys 12 order burger or bunch of muffin it s me !! You guys always made order really fast and accurate. And thank you so much for the free cookie

This McDonalds location goes out of their way to make EVERY customer feel special and ensure that all orders are awesome. Manager Marvin exemplifies excellent customer service beyond the call of duty.
Very convenient 24h service collect 7 stickers and get free coffee
Very fast service and friendly staff. I find their coffee tastes better than other locations. Perhaps coz of high volume and it being fresher?

Honestly the best McDonalds in the city. Its efficiently run, tons of leadership and management on hand. This is clearly a location that builds careers. Im just a customer, but Im always impressed with this location. I figured I should leave a positive review.
They can make both good and bad food,  maybe they see if the person ordering has come out of a bentley or not. I swear I saw the manger looking at CCTV for same. She was nice to me though
Always a great experience, nice people, good food, good service. I love the LCD touch screens to order, and skipping the line while you just wait for your meal. Great idea McDonalds!
Fantastic dinner! The beef was tender, the potatoes cooked to perfection... I thought the drinks were pricey but this is how it goes in Vancouver...  I think it really impressed my date!
6 June 2020 For this particular visit, curb side pick up went smoothly and order was correct. I even got a heart shaped choco chip cookie. Good job team
Russel, the manager is very kind, compassionate, polite and down to earth person. He went above and beyond for me. McDonalds, you are lucky to have him.
Its a McDonalds, what else is there to say? Super quick service, cheap, and tasty. Best hot $8 meal you can get.
Pretty good drive thru. Never any problems getting my order quickly during my lunch breaks.
really fast and the workers are nice food was good too
With app it was pretty nice since no need to remember to bring a paper coupon and could just park and wait for the food to be made.
Hottest coffee Ive ever had at any McDonalds friendly service, air conditioning to escape the heat from :D
The place is very good, they serve food fast, the allow you to get paper (not like the Metrotown one), the food isn t served messy, the best McDonald s I have been to.
I truly recommend this location the service is first class and the staff are very professional and friendly. Plus the sandwiches they make are a 10 out of 10. Im a customer from now on.
Very fast service had to take time to clean between each customers for covid-19 and you can actually eat inside this McDonalds nice.
Great experience with a big breakfast order for Nurses Week. Staff was friendly and accommodating. Everything went very smoothly. Would order there again.
Great place after renovation. Table service is cool. Each booth has an outlet, which is good for studying, pretty nice ambiance.
Love their McDoubles. It is amazing
Excellent open concept restaurant with bright and comfy seating areas. Very busy drive thru!
Unlike other locations they have a full menu of food available
You cant go wrong with Mcdonalds fast food but the staff is a hit and missed kind of service!
Love the coffee. Unbeatable coffee + muffin combo deal! Plz make coffee + bagel the same price as with muffin because muffins are probably really unhealthy.
Kulwinder singh is a best employee over here. He has quick capacity to deal all customers with very good manners.
I dont eat McDonalds very much, but the drive-thru service here is always SO friendly! Which I think is super rare for fast food places
Big parking lot and friendly staffs.  The drive thru lane is almost always busy but the staffs are fast and efficient, so you could expect to get in and out fast.
One of the best McD locations Ive been to. Very busy but always well staffed and prompt service.
Ordered from mobile for pickup in the parking lot. My order was finished in a jiffy. Very satisfied with the service at this location!
The usual mcd menu but very clean including bathrooms, plenty of dining space + drive thru & mobile order, uber eats. also plenty machine kiosks and friendly & professional staff
Im totally impressed
I love that these guys are flexible and willing to lettuce wrap my burgers for me. Good price fast food and pleasant service.
Amazing staff always go the extra mile, even sending an extra treat and leaving nice notes on the bag for delivery orders!
What can I say that hasnt been said by others? Great for a quick junk food fix. Their McChicken burgers went downhill since the beginning.
One of my favorite McDonalds.. clean, well lit and friendly staff. Bathroom is quite clean (compared with others).
If youre going to eat here, make sure its through the drive through. In-store visit is a no no unless you feel like being harassed.
Its McDonald, you get what you get from here.  If you dont know what McDonald s is all about, you should probably climb out from underneath the rock you been living under.
didn t screw up order got my nuggies
Michael Song is the best !!! So patient, kind and makes sure all your sauce needs are taken care of. #sauceitup
Central location. Bad or no service. 20 mins waiting time for both drive thru and dine in.
Fast and efficient service. Drive through can be crowded at times but its not a fault of the establishment.
The place is clean & beautiful after renovation.  Staff are friendly & so efficient.   Not bad at all!
Fast food as expected
Service was meh but the icecream was on point
I recommend the hamburger. Also, poor choice of hats at this location.
The place is always really clean. They have a lot of the touchscreen ordering stations as well.
This is seriously a great McDonalds. From the Manager Ricky on down, the most consistantly high quality McDonalds Ive been to in a long while.

hasnt been too ghetto for me yet. They allowed me in even when my head was covered with saran wrap during a late night hair dyeing day.
old work place has received an update.  comple renovation
Nice employees, but its one of the most busiest McDs I have been to.
